# Popup UI Module

## PURPOSE
Main popup window that appears when user clicks extension icon.
Primary interface for scanning inbox and viewing subscriptions.

## CONTAINS
- popup.html: Main popup HTML structure
- popup.js: Popup logic and event handlers
- popup.css: Popup-specific styles

## FEATURES
- Scan button to trigger inbox scan
- Subscription list display
- Unsubscribe link buttons
- Authentication status
- Payment prompt (after 5 free subs)
- Loading states
- Error messages

## UI FLOW
1. User opens popup
2. Check if authenticated -> show login if not
3. Check payment status
4. Show scan button
5. On scan: show loading -> display results
6. If >5 subs and not paid: show payment prompt
7. Display unsubscribe links for each subscription

## REFERENCES
- Parent: /src/ui/.windsurf
- Root: /.windsurf
- Uses: /src/core/*, /src/api/*

## RULES
- Keep popup lightweight (fast load time)
- Show clear CTAs (Call To Action)
- Handle offline state gracefully
- Provide feedback for all user actions
